As a user
I need to be able to reset my password
So that I can regain access to my account if I forget my password

Details and Assumptions
* The user has already registered an account with the system
* The system has an email service to send password reset instructions
Acceptance Criteria
gherkin
Given a registered user
When I click on the "Forgot Password" link
Then I should receive an email with instructions on how to reset my password
And the email should contain a unique password reset link
